ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 保安區都有好多人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c874e848814a173c1e869695480a30a988cfb1","tid":347733,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>圍頭話相信少之又少<br />\n客家話我估就有少少</blockquote><br />\n好想知香港仲有幾多個後生識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前EU播緊果陣d人咪識多少少"},{"pid":"9b5add9f2c114e259508591aab4652efa4d71989","tid":347733,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我識圍頭話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想好奇統計一下你幾歲？"},{"pid":"9c518d1d3b94a05de4e5cf7c5555b5d8d9327045","tid":347733,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:56:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>圍頭話相信少之又少<br />\n客家話我估就有少少</blockquote><br />\n好想知香港仲有幾多個後生識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前EU播緊果陣d人咪識多少少</blockquote><br />\n呢套劇的確引起到多左人對呢個語言嘅興趣，但硬係有啲發音去得唔夠盡，仲差少少鄉下佬嘅韻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過睇得出SignalWong應該下過苦工去學講同忍笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過劇已完，唔知仲有幾多人會對呢個語言有興趣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89130022226bf6e5e16278a7aebd7c0a5c6e7254","tid":347733,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:06:16.000Z","msg":"見到衣家啲細路擔心語言消失，不如想想如何將它好好保存，因為我們對語言的態度"},{"pid":"9d4cfd43b2d537d08e4a70da3d14d6eb4dd005e9","tid":347733,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到衣家啲細路擔心語言消失，不如想想如何將它好好保存，因為我們對語言的態度</blockquote><br />\n未打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我想講見到衣家啲細路受到普教中嘅摧殘，好擔心廣東話嘅未來，更何況係已經無咩人識嘅圍頭話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 語言係文化傳承嘅橋樑，承載著一個族群的文化，所以好擔心語言消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0018bd83c658d754252d5607c763d8434d23b643","tid":347733,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識聽 唔識講<br />\n利申 圍頭牛屎仔</blockquote><br />\n幾歲？<br />\n點解識聽唔識講嘅？因為屋企人會講但少講？定係無興趣去學講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}